{"tid":1804081,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"除夕夜藝人倒數活動全軍覆沒","createTime":"2019-12-30T16:55:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T17:43:19.000Z","uid":5195,"like":34,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"942c95f0c71988d001afb0d242be36ec0fe02abe","tid":1804081,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"不經不覺，香港人反抗已經持續半年有多，反送中、反監控、對抗制度暴力、警察暴力、白衣人恐襲、高官們的白色恐怖&hellip;&hellip;戰線多不勝數。香港民意研究所調查發現，2019年是27年來香港人最不快樂的一年，剛過去的聖誕節氣氛全無，皆因香港人全心為未來拼搏。<br />\n<br />\n明日除夕夜，以往無論電視台抑或商場都會舉行倒數活動，不過今年卻例外，藝人將會集體放假，因為明晚沒有任何活動通告，藝人倒數活動全軍覆沒！另外，今日繼續有人在討論區狙擊TVB，號召網民抵制有TVB藝人包括譚凱琪、張秀文等出席的地區倒數活動，不過該活動大前日已經因「近期社會狀況」而取消，TVB亦為此變陣，明晚將以《後生仔傾吓傾吓傾到2020》節目跨年。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cedbabb3fb41d202e0ed3a9f4425d00d5290c99","tid":1804081,"uid":42548,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:58:15.000Z","msg":"喺，，，唔出活動無收入，等炒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8b0d72340f91f3a06293de7b71f9c44c6e63200","tid":1804081,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:58:52.000Z","msg":"支持cctvb收皮"},{"pid":"505ffc69fb5697797299dacbccff71ff48b5fae0","tid":1804081,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9cedbabb3fb41d202e0ed3a9f4425d00d5290c99","tid":1804081,"uid":42548,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:58:15.000Z","msg":"喺，，，唔出活動無收入，等炒啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T16:59:07.000Z","msg":"仲有廣告，訪問好多樣野"},{"pid":"ad5d7df047a9cae5f258e2b1e7b7551c33bd5891","tid":1804081,"uid":191527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T17:04:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61091288faceb3d3e17cfafe719bfaf5ca5d8dc","tid":1804081,"uid":76310,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9cedbabb3fb41d202e0ed3a9f4